item.title: Bands?
item.dc:creator: @Elrick Elrick
item.description:
@Elrick wrote:

Might have been better to make this an artist top 5, but oh well lol.

  1. Black Sabbath

  2. Jimi Hendrix

  3. Linkin Park

  4. Rage Against the Machine

  5. Metallica

  6. Sabbath’s Symptoms of the Universe was my first ever album

  7. Hendrix was introduced by Dave Matthews Band, which my dad showed me the original version and I got turned onto the Classic Rock genre

  8. Linkin Park’s Meteora was the first ever album I bought with my own money

  9. RAtM is all the anger and frustration I could want in music

  10. Metallica’s Sad But True is one of the best songs in existence (IMO)
